===Overview===
The '''Conservative Party''', officially the Conservative and Unionist Party, and also known colloquially as the Tories or simply the Conservatives, is a centre-right political party in the [[United Kingdom]]. 

===Events===
[[James Jaspers (Earth-616)|Sir James Jaspers]] was a Conservative (MP) for [[Haslope West]].{{r|Daredevils #7}} He  won a landslide general election victory due to his Anti-Superhuman stance.{{r|Daredevils #9}}
